frames.caption: A surreal scene depicts a surfer riding a wave inside a room, with a large window framing a vibrant sunset. The wave curls dramatically, creating a striking contrast against the warm glow of the setting sun. The room is furnished with a desk, computer, and wall art, blending the indoor setting with the outdoor adventure.
